reviewText: Some things were not in the cloud workspace .

It's ok, I learned something new, new approach. In the beginning you need to adjust webdriver version by yourself because Chrome updated automatically.In my case, script was too fast and couldn't find elements and I needed to modify the script with wait(s).
That was great experience for me. Saurabh Dhingra explains very well. I refreshed my knowledge. Thank you!
Just right to learn basics of using Selenium on e-commerce website.
